properties.Name: CustomerTelephoneNumber
properties.Description: The customer telephone number of the associated Telephone Number Type for the indicated period.

Columns.Name: CustomerId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Customer.

Columns.Name: TelephoneNumberTypeId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Telephone Number.

Columns.Name: TelephoneNumber
Columns.Description: The complete, concatenated telephone number (area code + prefix + suffix + extension).

Columns.Name: PeriodStartTimestamp
Columns.Description: The period start timestamp associated with the information.

Columns.Name: PeriodEndTimestamp
Columns.Description: The period end timestamp associated with the information.

Columns.Name: PreferenceId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Preference.

Columns.Name: TelephoneNumberNote
Columns.Description: A note, comment or additional information regarding the Telephone Number.

Columns.Name: LocationId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Location.

Columns.Name: TextCapableIndicator
Columns.Description: Indicates whether the telephone (number) is capable of sending / receiving text messages.
